{
	quest.04833C4BB0CCCBB7.quest_desc: ["Same as Stone Weapons just the &7Sword &rwill Drop &eAmbrosium Shards&r when Hitting Mobs and the &7Axe&r will drop them when chopping down &2Trees&r."]
	quest.04833C4BB0CCCBB7.title: "&7Holystone&r Weapons"
	quest.0483D3B051665F07.quest_desc: ["&5Zanite&r gets a whole lot more uses than the other Items before it. \\n\\nWe can make Tools and Armor out of it. \\n\\nEven special Items like &5Nature Staff&r and an &5&lAltar&r."]
	quest.0483D3B051665F07.title: "&5Zanite"
	quest.04B92FAB179A74C9.quest_desc: ["The &dGravitite Sword&r will toss whatever it Hits in the Air. Like Knockback... just up! \\n\\nThe &dGravitite Axe&r is the only way to cut down &eGolden Oak Trees&r. "]
	quest.04B92FAB179A74C9.title: "&dGravitite&r Weapons"
	quest.08788F976B5C3281.quest_desc: ["The &6Holy Sword&r is like a &bDiamond Sword&r with Smite on it. \\n\\nSmite does extra Damage to Undead Mobs. So does the &6Holy Sword&r. \\n\\nBest part is, you can Enchant it with Smite to add even more Damage!"]
	quest.08788F976B5C3281.title: "&6Holy Sword"
	quest.08E4892F96828EC4.quest_desc: [
		"You can't Hit the &c&lSun Spirit&r, to start a Fight with him you'll need to Right Click him to talk to him. \\n\\nDo it a few more times... then a few more... then after a dozen extra he'll be angered enough to start the fight! \\n\\nThe &c&lSun Spirit&r will begin to wander around the room spreading &cFire&r wherever he goes. \\n\\nHe will also shoot &cFire Crystals&r and &bIce Crystals&r. In order to deal Damage to him you'll need to Hit the &bIce Crystals&r at him to Freeze him! Once Frozen you can finally Hit him. \\n\\nAfter being Frozen he'll also summon &cFire Minions&r to help him. \\n\\nOnce he is put out he'll Drop..."
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/aether/aether_gold2.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.08E4892F96828EC4.title: "&c&lSun Spirit"
	quest.0D2BF2C5D784FCBE.quest_desc: ["The &eValkyrie Cape&r will act like a Slow Falling Potion. \\n\\nHelpful for &e&lThe Aether&r and &d&lThe End&r!"]
	quest.0D2BF2C5D784FCBE.title: "&eValkyrie Cape"
	quest.0D2F07FC0F804223.quest_desc: [
		"Bring her the 10 &eVictory Medals&r and now you can fight her! \\n\\nThe &e&lQueen&r has 500 &4Hearts&r. She'll dash around the room swinging her Sword at you. \\n\\nSometimes she'll throw Thunders Crystals at you that will summon Lightning which 1. should be impossible because of the roof and 2. is definitely cheating. \\n\\nOnce beaten in Battle she'll give her &eGold Sword&r and..."
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/aether/aether_silver2.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.0D2F07FC0F804223.title: "&e&lValkyrie Queen"
	quest.102DD961706E861A.quest_desc: ["&5Aechor Plants&r are Hostile living Plants. Wait all Plants are living... well these have 7 and a Half &4Hearts&r which other &2&lMinecraft&r Plants don't. \\n\\n&5Aechor Plants&r will shoot out Arrows which if they hit you, you'll get the &5Inebreviation Effect&r. It acts as a Poison mixed with Nausea and a whole new Effect. \\n\\nWhen Killed they'll Drop their &5Petal&r."]
	quest.102DD961706E861A.title: "&5Aechor Plant"
	quest.1B7B377CB757867E.quest_desc: ["All &dGravitite Tools&r can be Right Clicked on their specific Blocks they break to blast them off into the Sky! \\n\\nThey're also the best Tools &l&eThe Aether&r has to offer."]
	quest.1B7B377CB757867E.title: "&dGravitite&r Tools"
	quest.1ECAEC7BE573BB9C.quest_desc: ["The &5&lAltar&r is a very useful Block. \\n\\nIt can &5Enchant&r Items and Repair &e&lAether&r or &2&lVanilla&r Tools. \\n\\nWhen it says Enchant it doesn't mean the &2&lVanilla&r Enchantments with Books. It just transforms certain &e&lAether&r Items! \\n\\nThe fuel for the &5&lAltar&r is &eAmbrosium&r."]
	quest.1ECAEC7BE573BB9C.title: "&5&lAltar"
	quest.1F446EF3AD20DC6B.quest_desc: ["This &5Hammer&r is both a ranged and Melee Weapon. \\n\\nYou can bash Mobs like normal, or Right Click to Shoot Projectiles. \\n\\nThe Projectiles will toss back Mobs like Breezeballs and will do Damage."]
	quest.1F446EF3AD20DC6B.title: "&5Hammer of Kingbdogz"
	quest.20C2A09007E1309A.quest_desc: ["&dGravitite Ore&r doesn't get Smelted, instead it gets &5Enchanted&r with the &5&lAltar&r. \\n\\nOnce &5Enchanted&r we can make Tools and Armor with it. Plus a Jukebox!"]
	quest.20C2A09007E1309A.title: "&dGravitite"
	quest.20D957B3C350CDE2.quest_desc: ["&dGravitite Armor&r has 20 Armor Points and 8 Armor Toughness. \\n\\nWhen wearing all 5 Pieces (yes, the &dGloves&r count too) you won't jump into the air, you'll leap! \\n\\nIt will also prevent Fall Damage too!"]
	quest.20D957B3C350CDE2.title: "&dGravitite&r Armor"
	quest.242C183437A4CCD4.quest_desc: ["&7Sentry Boots&r negate all Fall Damage!"]
	quest.242C183437A4CCD4.title: "&7Sentry Boots"
	quest.24E124F12CFF2A50.quest_desc: [
		"The &7&lSlider&r is the Boss of the &7Bronze Dungeon&r. \\n\\nIt's a Cube... It has 400 &4Hearts&r and you'll need a Pickaxe to deal Damage. The better the Pickaxe the more Damage. \\n\\nThe &l&7Slider&r is very simple, he only moves one way at a time and only a few Blocks. Very easy to avoid. \\n\\nOnce you get him to 100 &4Hearts&r his Eyes will turn &4Red&r and he'll move faster. \\n\\nIf you \"Mine\" him you'll get..."
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/aether/aether_bronze2.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.24E124F12CFF2A50.title: "&l&7The Slider"
	quest.26D6FC091B7A8B38.quest_desc: ["The &eSilver Key&r! \\n\\nThe Treasure Chest opens up beneath the &e&lQueen's&r Throne."]
	quest.26D6FC091B7A8B38.title: "&eSilver Key"
	quest.27F62C4B42B16015.quest_desc: ["Just place a 4x5 &eGlowstone Rectangle&r, just like a &cNether Portal&r and pour &9Water&r in it to make the &eAether Portal&r? \\n\\nYeah right, I'm not 7, I'm not falling for that again! "]
	quest.27F62C4B42B16015.title: "&eAether Portal"
	quest.29E6EFC8C19912BD.quest_desc: ["&7Sentries&r are a hybrid of &aSlimes &fand &aCreepers&r. \\n\\nThey bounce like &aSlimes&r and EXPLODE like &aCreepers&r! \\n\\nIf you Kill them before they blow up, they'll Drop &7Carved Stone&r."]
	quest.29E6EFC8C19912BD.title: "&7Sentries"
	quest.2E05F4FB1A1FDE2D.quest_desc: ["&9Blue Swets&r have 6 &4Hearts&r. \\n\\nThey won't Damage you... well by themselves. Instead they'll capture you and leap high into the air bringing you with. \\n\\nWhen captured the only way to free yourself is to Hit them. \\n\\nOn Death &9Blue Swets&r will Drop &9Swet Balls&r and &bBlue Aeroclouds&r."]
	quest.2E05F4FB1A1FDE2D.title: "&9Blue Swet"
	quest.31A2B9C5C0962160.quest_desc: ["Fire Aspect &bDiamond Sword&r."]
	quest.31A2B9C5C0962160.title: "&cFlaming Sword"
	quest.326452FFA7F5C6CA.quest_desc: ["&eGolden Swets&r act like &9Blue Swets&r. Same Health, same Attack. \\n\\nJust these guys can survive higher Jumps, which means they'll Jump more times and higher than &9Blue Swets&r. \\n\\n&eGolden Swets&r will Drop &eGlowstone&r! Helpful for recreating the &ePortal&r."]
	quest.326452FFA7F5C6CA.title: "&eGolden Swet"
	quest.3417FF406CF0479E.quest_desc: ["&2Skyroot&r is the only Tree we find besides &eGolden Oak&r. \\n\\nThere's also Crystal Trees but those also use &2Skyroot Logs&r so same difference! \\n\\n&2Skyroot&r like any Logs can make Blocks, Tools, ETC."]
	quest.3417FF406CF0479E.title: "&2Skyroot Trees"
	quest.34FBB18ADA647010.quest_desc: ["The Cloud Staff will summon 2 Cloud Minions that orbit you when you Right Click. \\n\\nIf you Left Click after Spawning them they both will shoot Ice Crystals at where you aim. \\n\\nOnce you're tired of them, just Shift Right Click to get rid of them."]
	quest.362F529D5E7C37A4.quest_desc: ["If you stand in &9Water&r with &6Phoenix Armor&r you'll get &5Obsidian Armor&r. \\n\\n&5Obsidian Armor&r gives up the Fire Protection for an extra 4 Armor Toughness."]
	quest.362F529D5E7C37A4.title: "&5Obsidian Armor"
	quest.3666C6DA23E15F78.quest_desc: ["A Bow that sets all Arrows on &cFIRE&r!"]
	quest.3666C6DA23E15F78.title: "&6Phoenix Bow"
	quest.36D9FB96D3557266.quest_desc: ["&9Moa's&r are big friendly Birds. \\n\\nThey have 17 and a &4Half Hearts&r and Drop Feathers. \\n\\nRandomly they'll Drop &9Moa Eggs&r which is how you'll be able to Tame them. Check out the &c&lIncubator&r to find out more!"]
	quest.36D9FB96D3557266.title: "&9Moa"
	quest.3781DB4807A89375.quest_desc: ["The&5 Zanite Sword&r is around Iron Sword Damage... until it losses Durability. \\n\\nYep, the &5Sword&r will deal more Damage the less Durability it has! \\n\\nThe &5Axe&r will chop &2Trees&r faster the less Durability it has."]
	quest.3781DB4807A89375.title: "&5Zanite&r Weapons"
	quest.3887FD4B14BB993D.quest_desc: ["&cRegeneration Stones&r will constantly Heal you when worn. \\n\\nYou can actually hold two of them and they will stack Healing!"]
	quest.3887FD4B14BB993D.title: "&cRegeneration Stone"
	quest.38E3ABEEFCE6A0B9.quest_desc: ["The &9Shield of Repulsion&r, when worn, will deflect Projectiles away from you and back at whoever threw them. \\n\\nIt has Durability though..."]
	quest.38E3ABEEFCE6A0B9.title: "&9Shield of Repulsion"
	quest.39E1211455224291.quest_desc: ["&bZephyrs&r are angry Clouds. \\n\\nWith only 2 and a &4Half Hearts&r they'll shoot Airballs at you. Like a Ghast, that shoots Breezeballs. \\n\\nWhen Killed they'll Drop Cold Aeroclouds."]
	quest.39E1211455224291.title: "&bZephyr"
	quest.3A8AF52A5AE7C6CB.quest_desc: ["It gives Water Breathing."]
	quest.3A8AF52A5AE7C6CB.title: "&7Iron Bubble"
	quest.3C62EDBB44D83A41.quest_desc: ["The &5Nature Staff&r works with Tamed &9Moas&r. \\n\\nWant them to Sit? Use the &5Staff&r."]
	quest.3C62EDBB44D83A41.title: "&5Nature Staff"
	quest.3DB036804AD70497.quest_desc: ["The &7Bronze Key&r! \\n\\nThe Treasure Chest is below where the &7&lSlider&r was sitting Dormant."]
	quest.3DB036804AD70497.title: "&7Bronze Key"
	quest.3EE51A812E593135.quest_desc: ["The &c&lIncubator&r has one job, hatch &9Moa Eggs&r. \\n\\nIt uses &eAmbriosium Torches&r as Fuel. You'll need 2 for each &9Egg&r to hatch. \\n\\nOnce the &9Egg&r hatches, a baby&9 Moa&r will Spawn! \\n\\nIt'll take 20 Minutes to grow up but once it grows up you can ride it with a Saddle. You can also command them with the &5Nature Staff&r."]
	quest.3EE51A812E593135.title: "&c&lIncubator"
	quest.3FE994532AF53ABB.quest_desc: ["Unlike its younger brother, the &3Lightning Sword&r acts like a normal Sword. \\n\\nJust anything it Hits will be struck with Lightning!"]
	quest.3FE994532AF53ABB.title: "&3Lightning Sword"
	quest.40AD1851C6851925.quest_desc: ["Haha! Somebody fell! \\n\\nHope you brought something to break your fall. \\n\\nNext time, just use the &ePortal&r!"]
	quest.40AD1851C6851925.title: "Whoops!"
	quest.4394AEF0823FB4D2.quest_desc: ["Same tier as Wooden Tools so it can't break Iron or &5Zanite Ore&r. \\n\\nBut Each &2Skyroot&r doubles Drops. \\n\\n&2Skyroot Pickaxe&r doubles Ores, &2Shovel&r doubles Dirt, and &2Hoe&r doubles Plant Drops."]
	quest.4394AEF0823FB4D2.title: "&2Skyroot&r Tools"
	quest.48530C6C1187F613.quest_desc: ["Aerogel is made by placing down &cLava&r in &l&eThe Aether&r. \\n\\nIt won't break from Explosions and can be made into other decoration!"]
	quest.4974F265003DAEC9.quest_desc: ["&eValkyrie Tools&r are like normal Tools just with double the Reach!"]
	quest.4974F265003DAEC9.title: "&eValkyrie Tools"
	quest.4AED9EF9E0F68483.quest_desc: ["The &7Holystone Pickaxe&r can Mine &5Zanite&r but not &dGravitite&r. \\n\\nAll of these Tools will randomly Drop &eAmbrosium Shards&r when Breaking Blocks."]
	quest.4AED9EF9E0F68483.title: "&7Holystone&r Tools"
	quest.4BF7F82F1C8680B9.quest_desc: [
		"The &7Bronze Dungeon&r is the easiest and simplest Dungeon. \\n\\nIt spawns underground and is made of big square rooms made of &7Carved Stone&r. You can find it by looking for Mossy Holystone above ground and following it down. \\n\\nEach room will Spawn &7Sentries&r and the Boss room will hold the &7&lSlider&r."
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/aether/aether_bronze1.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.4BF7F82F1C8680B9.title: "&7Bronze Dungeon"
	quest.4E847B0288265DA3.quest_desc: ["&dCockatrice&r look like &9Moas&r just with Glowing Eyes and Feathers. \\n\\nThese feathered foes Spawn in the Dark only. \\n\\nThey'll spit at you, when it Hits it'll give you the &5Inebreviation Effect&r. Look at the &5Aechor Plant&r for a better description of that Effect. \\n\\n&dCockatrice&r have 10 &4Health&r and Drop Feathers when slain."]
	quest.4E847B0288265DA3.title: "&dCockatrice"
	quest.4F2DB9CDE2BACB69.quest_desc: ["This Quest has been authored by &6AllTheMods Staff&r, or a &2Community contributor&r for use in AllTheMods Modpacks. \\n\\nAs all &6AllTheMods&r packs are licensed under &eAll Rights Reserved&r, this Quest is not allowed to be used in any public packs not released by &6AllTheMods Team&r without explicit permission. \\n\\nThis quest is intentionally hidden, if you're seeing this, you're in editing mode."]
	quest.52007C01B52F7295.quest_desc: ["&eValkyries&r spawn in the &eSilver Dungeon&r. \\n\\nYou'll need to beat 10 of them in order to fight the &e&lValkyrie Queen&r. \\n\\nThey have 50 &4Hearts&r each and are Neutral until you Hit them. Thankfully they'll fight one at a time."]
	quest.52007C01B52F7295.title: "10 &eVictory Medals"
	quest.57DD886985DBFD97.quest_desc: ["When opening Chests in Dungeons you may come across a fearsome fake, the &4Mimic&r. \\n\\n&4Mimics&r have 20 &4Hearts&r and deal a ton of Damage. \\n\\nDon't worry about your Loot you might have gotten from the Chest, when Killed the &4Mimic&r will Spawn similar Loot!"]
	quest.57DD886985DBFD97.title: "&4Mimic"
	quest.58006FC06C34F6CA.quest_desc: ["&5Zanite Armor&r gives a total of 15 Armor Points. \\n\\nNothing special about them, they're just Armor!"]
	quest.58006FC06C34F6CA.title: "&5Zanite&r Armor"
	quest.5825892699A8DCB7.quest_desc: ["Wow, it worked... \\n\\nWelcome to &e&lThe Aether&r one of the Modpacks from all of our childhoods! And yeah, it is just as we remember! \\n\\n&e&lThe Aether&r is a Sky Dimension, flying high above the &2&lOverworld&r. There's floating Islands and structures and clouds! Lots and lots of clouds. \\n\\nHere you'll also find new Items, Mobs, and even Dungeons."]
	quest.5825892699A8DCB7.title: "&l&eThe Aether"
	quest.5900ADCC247CD5F9.quest_desc: [
		"The &eSilver Dungeon&r is the easiest Dungeon to find because its above ground. \\n\\nAnd on huge Clouds. \\n\\nAnd made of &eAngelic Stone&r. \\n\\nIt is shaped like Greek Architecture, which is weird because &eValkyries&r are Norse. \\n\\nTo find the &e&lValkyrie Queen&r you need to go up to the top floor and find the staircase in the back and go down it. After talking to her she'll tell you to get 10 &eVictory Medals&r before you can fight her."
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/aether/aether_silver1.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5900ADCC247CD5F9.title: "&eSilver Dungeon"
	quest.5A5D4DFE4175FB42.quest_desc: [
		"The &cGold Dungeon&r is also found underground. \\n\\nThis time it is more noticeable as it spawns under a huge mound covered in &eGolden Oak Trees&r. \\n\\nThe Dungeon is pretty darn simple, it is just a room with the Boss in it."
		"{image:atm:textures/questpics/aether/aether_gold1.png width:200 height:100 align:center}"
	]
	quest.5A5D4DFE4175FB42.title: "&cGold Dungeon"
	quest.5BB5EE00BB4F9691.quest_desc: ["&7Flying Cows&r are Cows with wings! \\n\\nNot much new... \\n\\n5 &4Hearts&r, Drops Raw Beef and Leather, can be Milked. \\n\\nJust these will glide so they don't take Fall Damage."]
	quest.5BB5EE00BB4F9691.title: "&7Flying Cow"
	quest.5C6BA6BBEC75EB71.quest_desc: ["The &cGold Key&r! \\n\\nThe Treasure Chest opens up behind the wall opposite of the entrance."]
	quest.5C6BA6BBEC75EB71.title: "&cGold Key"
	quest.5F44BF9A1DAE8B99.quest_desc: ["&9Neptune Armor&r gives 15 Armor Points and 4 Armor Toughness. \\n\\nThis whole set will make you swim through &9Water&r quicker! That's it."]
	quest.5F44BF9A1DAE8B99.title: "&9Neptune Armor"
	quest.6149E5F1F9CF8DC6.quest_desc: ["The Phyg! (Is it still pronounced as pig?). \\n\\nWhen Pigs fly is now! The Pigs got Wings now. So they'll glide like Chickens to avoid Fall Damage. \\n\\nThey have 5 Hearts and will Drop Raw Porkchops and Feathers on Death."]
	quest.6149E5F1F9CF8DC6.title: "&dPhyg"
	quest.6188A57F52F29D33.quest_desc: ["Ever play Terraria? Remember the Life Crystals? These work pretty similar. \\n\\nWhen you use a &cLife Shard&r you'll gain an extra &4Heart&r! \\n\\nI don't know what the max &4Hearts&r is... when you find out let me know!"]
	quest.6188A57F52F29D33.title: "&cLife Shard"
	quest.63D4621C06BA747C.quest_desc: ["Same Damage as Wood Weapons but &2Skyroot&r gives Double Drops. \\n\\n&2Skyroot Sword&r will give twice the Drops from Mobs and &2Skyroot Axe&r will give twice the amount of Logs from &2Trees&r."]
	quest.63D4621C06BA747C.title: "&2Skyroot&r Weapons"
	quest.6797E67E0136D96A.quest_desc: ["&7Holystone&r is everywhere. It is the Stone of &e&lThe Aether&r. \\n\\nYou'll need a Pickaxe to Mine it, and you can make Tools or Blocks with it."]
	quest.6797E67E0136D96A.title: "&7Holystone"
	quest.6B3328B6AE8704D2.quest_desc: ["&bLightning Knives&r are thrown projectiles that will summon Lightning wherever they Hit! \\n\\nThey'll be used up when thrown though so use them wisely."]
	quest.6B3328B6AE8704D2.title: "&bLightning Knife"
	quest.6C8766679D0AA8F6.quest_desc: ["This Weapon will 1 Hit Pigs, Piglins, and Zombified Piglins. \\n\\n2 Hit Hoglins and Zoglins. \\n\\n3 Hit Piglin Brutes."]
	quest.6C8766679D0AA8F6.title: "&dPig Slayer"
	quest.6D2425DAEA1FC211.quest_desc: ["The &cSun Altar&r can change the time of &e&lThe Aether&r. \\n\\nYeah even though there is no Daylight Cycle in &l&eThe Aether&r, this little Block can change it. \\n\\nJust scroll to whenever you want! \\n\\nIf you turn it Nighttime then you can use a Bed in &l&eThe Aether&r to set a Respawn Point."]
	quest.6D2425DAEA1FC211.title: "&cSun Altar"
	quest.705AEEDA95C52C99.quest_desc: ["The &b&lFreezer&r does as the name suggests, it &bFreezes&r certain objects. \\n\\n&9Water &fto &bIce&f, &bIce &fto &bPacked Ice&f, &bPacked Ice &fto &9Blue Ice&r, and &cLava &fto &5Obsidian&r. \\n\\nThere's also Ice Rings and Pendants! \\n\\nThe &b&lFreezer&r uses Icestone as Fuel."]
	quest.705AEEDA95C52C99.title: "&b&lFreezer"
	quest.714960DF26EFFA53.quest_desc: ["All the &5Tools&r will Mine Blocks faster when they lose Durability. \\n\\nAlso the &5Pickaxe&r can Mine &dGravitite&r."]
	quest.714960DF26EFFA53.title: "&5Zanite&r Tools"
	quest.72133DD1B3237493.quest_desc: ["The &4Vampire Blade&r has Lifesteel. \\n\\nWhen Dealing Damage you'll Heal a little bit of &4Hearts&r in return!"]
	quest.72133DD1B3237493.title: "&4Vampire Blade"
	quest.7597D3D06E761759.quest_desc: ["The &eValkyrie Lance&r is a Melee Weapon with huge Reach! \\n\\n10 Blocks!"]
	quest.7597D3D06E761759.title: "&eValkyrie Lance"
	quest.75C5BFAEADEB486E.quest_desc: ["&eValkyrie Armor&r has the same Stats as &cNetherite Armor&r. \\n\\nThe fun part comes when you wear all of it at the same time: Helmet, Chestplate, Leggings, Boots, and Gloves. \\n\\nWhen wearing all 5 parts of it you can hold Space to Fly! Only for a short time though."]
	quest.75C5BFAEADEB486E.title: "&eValkyrie Armor"
	quest.765F6A5A9779CF6D.quest_desc: ["Aerclouds spawn all over &l&eThe Aether&r. I mean it is a sky Dimension, pretty much expected. \\n\\nCold Aerclouds and &eGolden Aerclouds&r work the same. You'll sink slightly into them. Kind of like &6Honey&r, just less Sticky. They also absorb Fall Damage. \\n\\n&bBlue Aerclouds&r are different though. If you bounce off of it you'll get boosted high into the sky. When Shifting you'll sink all the way through them. \\n\\nYou can pick up Aerclouds anywhere. You can also &5Enchant&r Cold Aerclouds to make &eGolden Aerclouds&r or &bFreeze&r Cold Aerclouds to make &bBlue Aerclouds&r."]
	quest.765F6A5A9779CF6D.title: "Aerclouds"
	quest.769B23E692CBA16B.quest_desc: ["These act like normal Buckets and Boats. \\n\\nJust from &l&eThe Aether&r!"]
	quest.769B23E692CBA16B.title: "&2Skyroot&r Boat and Bucket"
	quest.78AAFE5AF04A13AC.quest_desc: ["&bAerbunnys&r bounce around on Air. If you could, you would too! \\n\\nThey are Passive with only 3 &4Hearts&r. \\n\\nIf you're evil enough to Kill one, they'll Drop String."]
	quest.78AAFE5AF04A13AC.title: "&bAerbunny"
	quest.78BD3D4FBA42D3DC.quest_desc: ["Sheepuffs are silly little animals found in the Aether. \\n\\nThey look like normal Sheeps but sometimes they'll randomly bolt up in the air and slowly fall down. I don't know why, maybe it's fun! \\n\\nSometimes the Sheepuffs will puff up with extra Wool, these can be Sheared twice in a row! \\n\\nThey have 4 Hearts and Drop Raw Mutton and Wool."]
	quest.78BD3D4FBA42D3DC.title: "Sheepuff"
	quest.79A1A63BCE7A541B.quest_desc: ["The &bInvisibility Cloak&r will make you Invisible. As the name and Pop Culture suggests! \\n\\nMobs won't see you when you're Invisible unless you get too close or Hit them."]
	quest.79A1A63BCE7A541B.title: "&bInvisibility Cloak"
	quest.7A4B51313FB134EA.quest_desc: ["&6Phoenix Armor&r in total will give 20 Armor Points and 8 Toughness, same as &cNetherite&r. \\n\\nJust &6Phoenix Armor&r actually puts through on Fire Protection, as when you are wearing it you won't take Damage from &cFire &for &cLava&r! \\n\\nCareful walking into &9Water&r with it or you might end up with..."]
	quest.7A4B51313FB134EA.title: "&6Phoenix Armor"
	quest.7AD4ED72AC31D912.quest_desc: ["&3Aerwhales&r are huge, fast, flying, Passive Mobs in &l&eThe Aether&r. \\n\\nThey don't Drop anything on Death, they're just pretty."]
	quest.7AD4ED72AC31D912.title: "&3Aerwhale"
	quest.7BFB4DA68A7912E5.quest_desc: ["Ambrosium is the Coal of &e&lThe Aether&r. \\n\\nWe can make Torches out of it or use it as Furnace Fuel! \\n\\nYou can also use it on Aether Grass to Enchant it."]
	quest.7BFB4DA68A7912E5.title: "&eAmbrosium"
	quest.7D7BB45D84A4E94A.quest_desc: ["When wearing the &3Swet Cape&r, &9Swets&r will become Friendly! \\n\\nNow instead of getting captured, you can ride them safely. \\n\\nThey take a lot less Fall Damage when they aren't trying to kill you."]
	quest.7D7BB45D84A4E94A.title: "&3Swet Cape"
